title: [PSP] Super Stardust Portable [USA]
description:
Super Stardust Portable brings the PlayStation Network favorite, Super Stardust HD, to the PSP system. In this classic arcade shooter and cult favorite, the player&#039;s mission is simple: destroy everything in sight! Controlling a ship, the player must defeat enemy forces and save his home solar system from total annihilation. Based on Super Stardust HD, the game has been tuned and redesigned to take advantage of the unique power and features of the PSP system.

With five highly detailed 3D planets to save, hordes of enemies and asteroids to destroy, and various game play modes, Super Stardust Portable presents super intense action on the PSP system.

KEY FEATURES

    * Super Intense Action - With three awesome, upgradeable weapons, blast your way through massive hordes of enemies and intense boss battles.
    * Game Modes Galore - Plenty of modes to satsify your trigger finger needs, including Arcade Mode, Planets Mode, Endless Mode, Bomber Mode and more.
    * Specifically Redesigned for PSP - Based on Super Stardust HD with extensive tuning and redesigned controls, plus the brand-new gameplay mode Impact.
